        {
          "step_id": "06_safe_demo_complete",
          "type": "system_reply",
          "message": "üéØ **SAFE DEMO COMPLETE!**\n\nEven in read-only mode, Pipulate offers powerful automation capabilities. Thanks for being cautious!",
